PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,FA Canadian man accused of selling
OL,7,Flethal substances online to people who
OL,8,Fused them to end their own lives has
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to 14 charges of
OL,10,Fcounselling or aiding suicide.
OL,12,FKenneth Law appeared in court in
OL,13,FOntario on Friday to enter the plea
OL,14,Fand sentencing is expected to take
OL,15,Fplace in September.
OL,17,FCanadian prosecutors are withdrawing
OL,18,F14 murder charges in exchange for
OL,19,FLaw's plea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,FThe charges against him in the
OL,7,FCanadian court are related to 14
OL,8,Fpeople across Ontario who were between
OL,9,Fthe ages of 16 and 36.
OL,11,FCanadian police say he used a series
OL,12,Fof websites to market and sell sodium
OL,13,Fnitrite. The substance is commonly
OL,14,Fused to cure meats and can be deadly
OL,15,Fif ingested. Police say Law is
OL,16,Fsuspected of sending at least 1,200
OL,17,Fpackages to more than 40 countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,FBritain's National Crime Agency (NCA)
OL,7,Fhas said 79 deaths in the UK are
OL,8,Fattributable to products supplied by
OL,9,FLaw, while 112 deaths are linked to
OL,10,Fwebsites associated with Law.
OL,12,FAfter receiving intelligence from
OL,13,FCanadian authorities suggesting a
OL,14,Fnumber of Britons had been implicated
OL,15,Fin Law's scheme, the NCA spent three
OL,16,Fyears building a case for extradition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,FHowever, at a press conference on
OL,7,FFriday, the NCA warned that following
OL,8,Fhis sentence, it is unlikely that Law,
OL,9,F60, from Toronto, would ever be
OL,10,Fextradited to face punishment in the
OL,11,FUK.
OL,13,FBritish families of Law's victims have
OL,14,Fexpressed disappointment that the
OL,15,Fpoison seller will not be punished in
OL,16,Fthe UK and have called for a public
OL,17,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,FHowever, Damon Hayes, the head of the
OL,7,FNCA's International Corruption unit,
OL,8,Fsaid that Law's crimes against people
OL,9,Fin the UK had been included in the
OL,10,FCanadian prosecution.
OL,12,F"Following recent legal advice, it was
OL,13,Fdecided that including Law's UK
OL,14,Foffending in his Canadian sentencing
OL,15,Fwas the right course of action to
OL,16,Fsecure justice for victims and
OL,17,Ffamilies here," he told reporters.
OL,26,@yD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,F"Under Canadian law, it is likely that
OL,7,FKenneth Law could challenge
OL,8,Fextradition on the basis that he's
OL,9,Falready been sentenced for the same
OL,10,Foffences in his own country.
OL,12,F"It's only due to the thoroughness and
OL,13,Fstrength of our investigation that's
OL,14,Fmeant this course of action is
OL,15,Favailable.
OL,17,F"The UK is the only country globally
OL,18,Fthat has an investigation detailed and
OL,19,Fmature enough to be included in the
OL,20,FCanadian prosecution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,F"The NCA has been working closely with
OL,7,Fpolicing colleagues in Scotland and
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland to ensure victims in
OL,9,Ftheir jurisdictions can also be
OL,10,Frecognised in this way in a Canadian
OL,11,Fcase."
OL,13,FHayes added that "victims and families
OL,14,Fhave been at the heart of all decision-
OL,15,Fmaking" and thanked them for their
OL,16,Fpatients throughout the "long and
OL,17,Fcomplex investigation".
OL,26,@sD@FO]xD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,F"We also want to acknowledge that the
OL,7,Floss families have suffered, and we
OL,8,Frecognise every family's experience of
OL,9,Floss is unique.
OL,11,F"We are also seeking to reflect the
OL,12,Fimpact of Law's crimes in victim
OL,13,Fimpact statements to be used in the
OL,14,Fsentencing process."
OL,16,FAndrew Hudson, a specialist prosecutor
OL,17,Fat the Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,18,Finsisted that "no victim has been left
OL,19,Fbehind as part of this process".
OL,26,@{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,FHe said UK authorities efforts "will
OL,7,Fensure that the full devastating
OL,8,Fextent of his criminal conduct is seen
OL,9,Fand considered by the sentence in
OL,10,Fcourt".
OL,12,F"An agreed statement of facts agreed
OL,13,Fbetween the prosecution and defence in
OL,14,FCanada will also document that Kenneth
OL,15,FLaw sent a total of 330 packages to
OL,16,F286 recipients in the UK.
OL,18,F"We say that all those recipients are
OL,19,Fvictims of Kenneth Laws' criminal
OL,20,Fenterprise."
OL,26,@nD@`OUrD@FO]|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,FHudson added: "By providing Canadian
OL,7,Fauthorities with evidence of Kenneth
OL,8,FLaw's offending, the pain and
OL,9,Fsuffering he caused to the victims in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales would be fully
OL,11,Frecognised."
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@sD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,FThe barrister told reporters that it
OL,7,Fwould have taken years to secure
OL,8,Fextradition, arguing that the sentence
OL,9,Fexpected in Canada is "likely to be
OL,10,Fsimilar" to what he would have faced
OL,11,Fin the UK.
OL,13,F"We are acutely aware of the added
OL,14,Fdistress that protracted extradition
OL,15,Fproceedings cause, and we were
OL,16,Fdetermined to avoid this while still
OL,17,Fdelivering an outcome that recognized
OL,18,Fthe immense suffering Kenneth Law
OL,19,Fcaused," he said.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,F"Ultimately the risk of an extradition
OL,7,Frequest being unsuccessful was too
OL,8,Fhigh, and the potential consequences
OL,9,Ftoo great for us to pursue this course
OL,10,Fof action.
OL,12,F"Kenneth Law is a serial offender who
OL,13,Fcallously exploited many vulnerable
OL,14,Fand innocent people exchanging their
OL,15,Flives for his financial gain.
OL,17,F"At the heart of this whole process
OL,18,Fhave always been the victims and
OL,19,Ffamilies who have suffered
OL,20,Funimaginable harm at his hands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780071066
OL,3,CCanadian poison seller linked to 79 UK
OL,4,Cdeaths pleads guilty to aiding suicide
OL,6,F"Ultimately, the approach we have
OL,7,Fagreed with our NCA and Canadian
OL,8,Fpartners will guarantee justice for
OL,9,Four victims in the quickest possible
OL,10,Fway, ensuring Kenneth Law is held
OL,11,Faccountable for the full extent of the
OL,12,Fdevastation he caused."
OL,14,FHow to get help if you are struggling
OL,15,Fwith your mental health
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
